Package: organizr
Title: Shortcuts for File Creation with Informative Prefixes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Johannes", "Brachem", , "jbrachem@posteo.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7884-4631"))
Description: Provides functions for quickly creating R scripts, as well as
    Rmarkdown or Quarto documents with automatically assigned name prefixes.
    Prefixes are either file counts (e.g. "001") or dates (e.g. "2022-09-26").
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
Imports: 
    fs,
    here,
    readr,
    rlang,
    rstudioapi,
    stringr
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
